      <title>韩国在2024年底在动荡中花费了大量捍卫胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/south-korea-spent-big-to-defend-won-amid-turmoil-in-late-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年年底，韩国在几个月后施加了最有力的胜利，以保护其经济免受强劲的美元和Yoon Suk Yeol总统对戒严事件的简短施加的市场溃败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/south-korea-spent-big-to-defend-won-amid-turmoil-in-late-2024</guid>
