      <title>高盛的Kostin再次针对增长风险再次削减S＆amp; P 500目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/goldman-slashes-s-p-500-target-for-second-time-on-growth-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街的预报员在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税截止日期之前几天就向美国股票发出了警报，高盛集团（Goldman Sachs Group Inc.）的戴维·科斯汀（David Kostin）在本月第二次削减了他的S＆amp; P 500目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/goldman-slashes-s-p-500-target-for-second-time-on-growth-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 06:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
